327	   * elements; otherwise a single-element array `[linkId]` identifying the
328	   * `link_model` row whose source contains the element. (Multi-hop transitive
329	   * links are deferred — the FED-01 expander is single-hop only.)
330	   */
331	  linkChainA?: string[];
332	  linkChainB?: string[];
333	};
